            </p>
          ]]>
                </translation>
                <translation language="en">
                    <![CDATA[
            <p>
              Register an application at <a href="https://dev.twitter.com/apps">https://dev.twitter.com/apps</a> to allow Fork CMS to connect with your Twitter account.<br />
              After registering your application, you should find the required consumer key & secret.<br />
              Make sure you enter a Callback URL (e.g. your website's url): this marks your Twitter application as "web app", which is required to complete the authentication.
            </p>
          ]]>
                </translation>
